name         'sycobuny-rvm'
version      '0.1.0'
summary      'Install and manage per-user RVM environments'
project_page 'https://github.com/sycobuny/puppet-rvm'
license      'BSD/MIT'
author       'Stephen Belcher ("sycobuny")'
description  <<DESC
This module will allow you to install RVM, RVM-managed rubies, and gemsets. It
can be configured to use non-standard directories and users, though it will,
by default, install to a given user's home directory.

For more usage information, please consult the README.md file provided with
the module.
DESC
